WEBVTT

00:00.668 --> 00:03.604
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:33.301 --> 00:35.769
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING,
CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

00:49.217 --> 00:52.286
THE CELEBRITY CULTURE MAKES
POLICE WORK IN LOS ANGELES

00:52.320 --> 00:54.755
DIFFERENT FROM ANYWHERE ELSE
IN THE COUNTRY.

00:54.788 --> 00:57.291
BUT ASK DETECTIVE LYDIA ADAMS
ABOUT IT,

00:57.325 --> 01:00.728
AND SHE'LL TELL YOU --
"CELEBRITY'S A BITCH."

01:00.761 --> 01:03.697
[ BED SPRINGS CREAKING ]

01:03.731 --> 01:07.201
[ SCOFFS ]

01:07.235 --> 01:09.570
[ SIGHS ]
OH, MY GOD.

01:09.603 --> 01:11.172
[ SCOFFS ]

01:11.205 --> 01:14.175
OH, NOT TONIGHT.
PLEASE!

01:14.208 --> 01:16.244
MOM!

01:16.277 --> 01:18.312
[ GROANS ]

01:18.346 --> 01:19.713
PBHT.

01:19.747 --> 01:22.283
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

01:26.487 --> 01:30.358
ADAMS.

01:30.391 --> 01:32.160
WAIT, HOLD ON, HOLD ON.

01:36.230 --> 01:38.232
ALL RIGHT, GO AHEAD.

01:41.369 --> 01:42.770
ALL RIGHT.

01:42.803 --> 01:44.472
[ SIGHS ]

01:44.505 --> 01:46.807
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS, THUDS ]

01:46.840 --> 01:48.176
[ SIGHS ]

01:49.643 --> 01:51.279
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

01:51.312 --> 01:52.813
[ CREAKING CONTINUES ]

01:52.846 --> 01:57.251
[ SCOFFS ]

01:57.285 --> 01:59.653
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

02:07.795 --> 02:09.263
[ GROANS ]

02:09.297 --> 02:11.399
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

02:13.267 --> 02:15.703
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

02:25.679 --> 02:27.448
[ PILLS RATTLE ]

02:30.684 --> 02:32.686
[ SIGHS ]

02:39.760 --> 02:41.295
[ SIGHS ]

02:41.329 --> 02:44.198
[ FOOTSTEPS POUNDING,
TREADMILL WHIRRING ]

03:15.996 --> 03:18.466
[ GROANS ]

03:29.943 --> 03:33.247
[ Sighing ] OHH.

03:33.281 --> 03:35.316
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:35.349 --> 03:37.785
GO BACK TO SLEEP, PETE.

03:37.818 --> 03:39.753
ARE YOU GOING TO WORK
TODAY?

03:43.957 --> 03:46.460
YEAH. I AM.

03:46.494 --> 03:49.630
ARE YOU GONNA GET KILLED
LIKE MY DAD?

03:52.300 --> 03:53.467
NO.

03:53.501 --> 03:55.503
[ BRAKES SQUEALING ]

04:11.819 --> 04:13.887
WASN'T THIS HOUSE
IN A SNOOP DOGG VIDEO?

04:13.921 --> 04:15.689
WHICH ONE?

04:15.723 --> 04:18.626
"LET'S GET BLOWN," I THINK.
THAT WAS MY JAM BACK IN THE DAY.

04:18.659 --> 04:20.828
[ CHUCKLES ] I LOST TRACK
AFTER "GIN AND JUICE."

04:20.861 --> 04:22.630
YOU KNOW, TONY --
HE ALWAYS PLAYED

04:22.663 --> 04:24.765
THAT "DOGGYSTYLE"
NONSTOP.

04:24.798 --> 04:25.966
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:25.999 --> 04:27.701
YOU LIKE SNOOP,
DETECTIVE ADAMS?

04:27.735 --> 04:29.370
YOU'RE FROM L.A., RIGHT?

04:29.403 --> 04:31.305
SNOOP D-O-DOUBLE-G IS
THE FIRST THING ON MY MIND

04:31.339 --> 04:32.973
AT THE SCENE
OF A DOUBLE AXE MURDER.

04:33.006 --> 04:34.808
[ CHUCKLES ]
WHO CALLED THIS IN
AGAIN?

04:34.842 --> 04:36.544
OH, A NOSEY NEIGHBOR.

04:36.577 --> 04:39.547
FLUFFY CAME HOME
WITH BLOOD ON HIS PAWS.

04:41.749 --> 04:45.386
OH, HEY.
WE CAN ALL GO HOME NOW.

04:45.419 --> 04:47.521
SHERLOCK HOLMES
ARRIVED.

04:47.555 --> 04:48.856
WHAT'S UP?

04:48.889 --> 04:50.724
CHIEF SENT ME.
SHE'S AT PARKER CENTER,

04:50.758 --> 04:52.460
PREPARING
FOR THE PRESS CONFERENCE.

04:52.493 --> 04:54.862
SHE WANTED ME TO COME,
CHECK THE SCENE OUT.

04:54.895 --> 04:56.797
WHY?

04:56.830 --> 04:59.099
I JUST DO
AS I'M TOLD.

04:59.132 --> 05:00.801
[ SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

05:00.834 --> 05:03.937
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

05:03.971 --> 05:05.839
BERT WILSON, R.H.D.

05:08.842 --> 05:10.744
JUST HIT TWITTER.

05:10.778 --> 05:13.814
BLOGGER MUST HAVE RECOGNIZED
THE ADDRESS.

05:13.847 --> 05:15.549
HERE COMES THE CIRCUS.

05:15.583 --> 05:17.851
WHAT'S UP WITH
LITTLE LORD FAUNTLEROY?

05:17.885 --> 05:20.688
[ CHUCKLES ] YOU DON'T KNOW
THE HALF, BROTHER.

05:20.721 --> 05:22.423
YOU GUYS ARE THE PRIMARIES
RIGHT NOW,

05:22.456 --> 05:24.024
BUT THIS CASE
IS GONNA GET TRANSFERRED

05:24.057 --> 05:26.026
TO ROBBERY AND HOMICIDE
AFTER YOU BRIEF WILSON.

05:26.059 --> 05:27.695
OH, THAT'S GREAT.

05:27.728 --> 05:29.430
WE GET ALL THE GUTS,
AND R.H.D. GETS ALL THE GLORY.

05:29.463 --> 05:31.465
THAT'S WHAT
WE'RE HERE FOR.

05:34.668 --> 05:38.138
THIS PLACE IS CRAZY.
WOW.

05:38.171 --> 05:41.442
OH, MAN.

05:41.475 --> 05:43.744
PHEW.

05:47.481 --> 05:51.452
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

05:51.485 --> 05:53.020
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

05:53.053 --> 05:56.089
IN CASE WE NEED A FEW ANGLES
THAT S.I.D. DOESN'T SHOOT.

06:03.497 --> 06:04.898
CAUGHT THAT?

06:04.932 --> 06:06.634
YEAH, LOOKS LIKE
A SNEAKER.

06:06.667 --> 06:08.869
AIR FORCE 1s.
I CAN TELL BY THE LOGO --

06:08.902 --> 06:10.904
MOST VERSATILE SNEAKER
EVER MADE.

06:12.773 --> 06:14.808
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

06:14.842 --> 06:16.577
[ SIREN WAILS ]

06:21.181 --> 06:23.116
I HEARD SHE GAVE KILLER HEAD,
BUT DAMN.

06:24.552 --> 06:26.053
WELL,
IT'S NOTHING PERSONAL.

06:26.086 --> 06:27.821
YOU GOT TO JOKE
ABOUT IT.

06:27.855 --> 06:29.557
YOU WANT TO FALL ASLEEP
THINKING ABOUT THAT ALL NIGHT?

06:29.590 --> 06:31.158
BASTARD
CUT HER HEAD OFF,

06:31.191 --> 06:33.561
AND YOU'RE TRYING OUT
FOR THE IMPROV?

06:33.594 --> 06:34.962
YOU OKAY?

06:34.995 --> 06:36.964
YEAH.

06:45.573 --> 06:48.208
SEE THAT TATTOO?

06:48.241 --> 06:49.943
BRITISH SPECIAL FORCES.

06:49.977 --> 06:52.546
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

06:52.580 --> 06:55.483
Lydia:
IT'S JUST ONE OF OURS.

06:58.686 --> 07:01.622
I THOUGHT THE HOUSE
WAS CLEARED.

07:04.224 --> 07:05.893
[ HANDLE RATTLES ]

07:09.597 --> 07:11.098
[ GUNS COCKING ]

07:24.912 --> 07:28.015
DON'T SHOOT!
DON'T SHOOT!

07:28.048 --> 07:30.217
[ CHILDREN WHIMPERING ]

07:30.250 --> 07:31.952
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

07:31.985 --> 07:33.220
WHAT'S YOUR NAME, BABY?

07:33.253 --> 07:34.588
CRISTINA.

07:34.622 --> 07:36.824
I CAN'T FIND MY DADDY.

07:36.857 --> 07:39.026
Taylor: I WANT MY DADDY.

07:48.969 --> 07:51.204
CAN I HELP YOU?
YES, OFFICER.

07:51.238 --> 07:53.040
I LIVE ON THIS STREET.

07:53.073 --> 07:54.274
REALLY?

07:54.307 --> 07:57.545
YOU GOT A LICENSE?

07:57.578 --> 07:59.279
SEE, I COULD LET YOU
ON THE STREET,

07:59.312 --> 08:01.281
BUT THEN I'D HAVE TO
SEARCH YOUR CAR,

08:01.314 --> 08:03.083
AND IF I SEARCHED YOUR CAR,
WELL...

08:03.116 --> 08:05.052
I MIGHT FIND
SOME CAMERA EQUIPMENT.

08:05.085 --> 08:06.920
AND IF I FOUND
SOME CAMERA EQUIPMENT,

08:06.954 --> 08:08.288
I'D HAVE TO CONFISCATE IT.

08:08.321 --> 08:11.825
YOU DON'T LIVE ON THIS STREET,
DO YOU?

08:11.859 --> 08:14.595
DO YOU EVEN HAVE
A PRESS I.D.?

08:16.196 --> 08:17.831
GET OUT OF HERE.

08:19.933 --> 08:21.935
GET HIM OUT.

08:29.943 --> 08:32.279
DETAIL IS CRAP.

08:34.347 --> 08:36.584
WHAT DO YOU SEE
EVERYWHERE YOU LOOK?

08:36.617 --> 08:37.951
PHOTOGRAPHERS.

08:37.985 --> 08:40.120
HELICOPTERS.

08:40.153 --> 08:41.955
COPS.

08:44.825 --> 08:47.327
COPS, STANDING AROUND
FOR HOURS,

08:47.360 --> 08:51.832
GUARDING SOME STREET FROM
THESE SHITBIRDS TAKING PICTURES

08:51.865 --> 08:54.267
FOR LONELY HOUSEWIVES
WHO ARE BORED OUT OF THEIR MINDS

08:54.301 --> 08:56.637
'CAUSE THEIR HUSBANDS
WON'T SCREW THEM ANYMORE.

08:58.171 --> 09:01.341
SHOULD BE OUT
DOING REAL POLICE WORK.

09:01.374 --> 09:03.076
[ BOTH SIGH ]

09:03.110 --> 09:05.078
YOU KNOW HOW MANY COPS
WERE DEPLOYED

09:05.112 --> 09:06.346
WHEN MICHAEL JACKSON DIED?

09:06.379 --> 09:08.081
BET YOU'RE GONNA
TELL ME.

09:08.115 --> 09:10.851
3,900.

09:10.884 --> 09:14.087
3,900.

09:14.121 --> 09:16.757
IT'S $1 MILLION IN SALARIES,
$2 MILLION IN OVERTIME.

09:16.790 --> 09:20.594
FOR WHAT? SO WE COULD WATCH
PEOPLE CRY OVER THAT...

09:20.628 --> 09:21.829
FREAK?

09:21.862 --> 09:23.697
[ Laughing ]
HEY, HEY. RELAX.

09:23.731 --> 09:25.699
I HAPPENED TO LIKE
THE GUY, OKAY?

09:25.733 --> 09:28.101
YEAH, ALL THAT
FOR THE "MAN IN THE MIRROR."

09:28.135 --> 09:30.838
GODDAMN WASTE.

09:30.871 --> 09:32.973
SAY WHAT YOU WANT,
BUT YOU KNOW HOW MANY CRIMES

09:33.006 --> 09:34.608
GOT COMMITTED
IN SOUTH CENTRAL

09:34.642 --> 09:37.110
DURING THE HOURS
OF THE FUNERAL?

09:37.144 --> 09:38.712
ZERO.

09:38.746 --> 09:40.614
EVEN THE GANGSTERS WERE HOME
WATCHING IT ON TV.

09:40.648 --> 09:41.782
[ CHUCKLES ]

09:43.150 --> 09:44.985
MORNING, LADIES.

09:45.018 --> 09:46.186
YEAH.

09:48.355 --> 09:51.191
YOU MIND IF I SMOKE?

09:51.224 --> 09:53.727
Lydia: YOUR HOUSE.

09:53.761 --> 09:55.896
Man: YOU GOT YOUR SILLY, LITTLE
ARREST WARRANT. FINE.

09:55.929 --> 09:58.398
BUT I'M NOT GONNA LET THIS
TURN INTO A FISHING EXPEDITION.

09:58.431 --> 10:00.267
THIS IS A POTENTIAL
CRIME SCENE.

10:00.300 --> 10:03.003
IF WE SEE OR HEAR ANYTHING
THAT WE CAN FIND USEFUL,

10:03.036 --> 10:04.404
YOU CAN'T STOP US.

10:04.437 --> 10:06.874
THEY DON'T HAVE SHIT.
DON'T ANSWER ANYTHING.

10:06.907 --> 10:08.942
Lydia: SO, YOU AND BETHANY
ARE DIVORCED?

10:08.976 --> 10:10.911
WE'RE STILL WORKING OUT
THE DETAILS.

10:10.944 --> 10:13.013
Josie: WHERE WERE YOU
LAST NIGHT?

10:13.046 --> 10:14.414
I WAS HERE.

10:14.447 --> 10:16.917
FELL ASLEEP AROUND 1:00.

10:16.950 --> 10:18.652
CAN ANYONE
VERIFY THAT?

10:20.053 --> 10:21.755
NICE SWORD
COLLECTION.

10:21.789 --> 10:23.023
THANK YOU.

10:23.056 --> 10:24.357
YOU'RE MISSING ONE.
WHAT HAPPENED TO IT?

10:24.391 --> 10:26.159
Man:
DON'T ANSWER THAT.

10:26.193 --> 10:28.662
SOMEBODY BROKE IN A WHILE AGO
AND STOLE SOME OF IT.

10:28.696 --> 10:30.097
ANYTHING ELSE MISSING?

10:30.130 --> 10:33.300
NOTHING I WANT TO TALK
TO THE POLICE ABOUT.

10:33.333 --> 10:35.035
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR HAND?
YOU CUT IT?

10:35.068 --> 10:36.704
I'VE BEEN TRAINING.

10:36.737 --> 10:39.172
I'M DOING TONY SCOTT'S
NEW MOVIE.

10:39.206 --> 10:41.108
WE'RE REMAKING
"SHOGUN ASSASSIN."

10:41.141 --> 10:43.911
IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME
SINCE I'VE HAD A GOOD MOVIE.

10:43.944 --> 10:46.313
THEY FLEW IN SONNY CHIBA HIMSELF
TO TRAIN ME.

10:46.346 --> 10:48.315
YOU KNOW WHO HE IS?
THIS IS MY BIG SHOT
AT COMING BACK.

10:48.348 --> 10:50.117
NO, IT WAS YOUR BIG SHOT.
COME ON.

10:50.150 --> 10:52.352
Bert: WE NEED TO MOVE HIM.
IT'S GETTING BAD OUT THERE.

10:52.385 --> 10:54.321
ALL RIGHT.
GIVE ME YOUR HAND, PLEASE.

10:54.354 --> 10:56.323
I DIDN'T DO IT.

10:56.356 --> 11:00.393
BETHANY'S THE ONLY WOMAN
I EVER LOVED.

11:00.427 --> 11:02.930
MY BABIES WERE IN THE HOUSE.

11:02.963 --> 11:04.832
C-C-CAN I SEE THEM?

11:04.865 --> 11:07.134
COME ON.

11:07.167 --> 11:11.739
I JUST GOT MY LIFE BACK.
WHY WOULD I [BLEEP] THIS UP NOW?

11:11.772 --> 11:15.743
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING,
CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

11:15.776 --> 11:17.845
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

11:26.754 --> 11:30.290
ALL THESE FLASHES?
NO WONDER KING KONG FLIPPED OUT.

11:32.025 --> 11:34.728
BACK UP! BACK UP!

11:41.534 --> 11:44.037
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

11:49.542 --> 11:51.411
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

11:54.882 --> 11:58.018
[ SIREN WAILS ]

12:04.157 --> 12:08.395
SO, WHAT DO WE
DO NOW?

12:08.428 --> 12:10.397
WE WAIT.

12:10.430 --> 12:11.932
FOR WHAT?

12:14.234 --> 12:16.269
YOU MEAN, WE STAND OUTSIDE
AN EMPTY HOUSE?

12:16.303 --> 12:19.139
YEAH. YEAH, 'CAUSE
MR. DREAMWORKS HIMSELF

12:19.172 --> 12:20.908
LIVES AT THE END
OF THAT STREET.

12:20.941 --> 12:23.010
AND ROCKY BALBOA
LIVES AT THE OTHER END.

12:23.043 --> 12:25.478
AND IF ONE OF THESE PAPARAZZIS
STEP ON THEIR AZALEAS,

12:25.512 --> 12:27.180
THE MAYOR'S PHONE'S
GONNA RING,

12:27.214 --> 12:29.016
THE CHIEF'S PHONE
AFTER THAT,

12:29.049 --> 12:31.451
AND THE WATCH COMMANDER'S PHONE
AFTER THAT, SO YOU TELL ME --

12:31.484 --> 12:33.553
WHICH DIRECTION DOES
THIS SHITSTORM ROLL IN?

12:33.586 --> 12:35.923
THIS IS YOUR NEW HOME...

12:35.956 --> 12:39.159
LIKE IT OR NOT.

12:39.192 --> 12:42.062
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

12:45.598 --> 12:47.968
THAT STUFF
WILL ROT YOUR BRAIN.

12:48.001 --> 12:50.037
YOU KNOW THEY PAY PEOPLE
FOR INFORMATION?

12:50.070 --> 12:52.039
YEAH, SO DO WE.
WHAT DOES THAT SAY ABOUT US?

12:52.072 --> 12:53.440
BESIDES, LOOK.

12:53.473 --> 12:55.175
IT'S GOT INFORMATION
ON VICTIM NUMBER TWO --

12:55.208 --> 12:58.912
BRITISH EX-COMMANDO BOY TOY,
CHARLES UPSON.

12:58.946 --> 13:01.982
LOOKS LIKE HE WAS GUARDING
HER BODY AND HER "BOOT-AY."

13:02.015 --> 13:04.484
IT SAYS RIGHT HERE THAT
"BILLY WAS FURIOUS ABOUT IT."

13:04.517 --> 13:06.086
MM.
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE

13:06.119 --> 13:08.188
WE'RE LOOKING AT BILLY STEARN
FOR THIS.

13:08.221 --> 13:11.058
MAN, HE'S BEEN A STAR
SINCE HE WAS 15.
I KNOW.

13:11.091 --> 13:13.193
LYDIA, LOOK.
LOOK AT HIS SNEAKERS.

13:13.226 --> 13:14.862
AIR FORCE 1s.

13:14.895 --> 13:16.229
YEAH, WE GOT TO LOOK
AT THESE

13:16.263 --> 13:18.198
AND SEE WHAT THEY LOOK LIKE
SPATTERED IN RED.

13:18.231 --> 13:20.333
HIS PARENTS?
OH, NO, THAT'S HERS.

13:20.367 --> 13:22.502
MOM LOOKS
JUST LIKE DAUGHTER, HUH?

13:22.535 --> 13:24.604
DAMN PAPPOS -- HOW'D THEY
GET HERE SO FAST?

13:24.637 --> 13:27.274
HOW'D THEY KNOW THAT THE KIDS
WERE AT THE CRIME SCENE?

13:27.307 --> 13:29.442
CELEBRITY DEATH
IN THE TWITTER AGE.

13:36.516 --> 13:38.185
[ SIREN CHIRPS ]

13:40.520 --> 13:42.089
LOOK AT THIS.

13:42.122 --> 13:44.157
THIS IS LIKE A ZOO.

13:44.191 --> 13:47.160
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING,
CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

13:52.265 --> 13:54.234
OH, MY GOSH.

13:54.267 --> 13:56.904
COME ON,
STAY BACK, STAY BACK.

13:56.937 --> 13:59.172
COME ON, JOSIE. I'LL
GIVE YOU 20 BUCKS IF
YOU HIT ONE OF THEM.
MOVE BACK, MOVE BACK.

13:59.206 --> 14:01.008
LET'S GO.
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GO.
ALL RIGHT.

14:09.682 --> 14:11.651
HEY, BRYANT.

14:11.684 --> 14:15.122
WELCOME BACK, BABY.

14:15.155 --> 14:17.524
GOOD TO SEE YOU.
HEY, I LIKE THIS.

14:17.557 --> 14:19.392
[ CHUCKLES ]
HEY, MAN.

14:19.426 --> 14:22.329
I'M GLAD TO SEE YOU GETTING
BACK UP ON THAT HORSE, SAM.

14:22.362 --> 14:24.131
CAN'T GET RID OF US ALL,
CAN THEY?

14:24.164 --> 14:25.933
YOU KNOW, LAST TIME
I SAW YOU SUIT UP

14:25.966 --> 14:27.567
WAS BACK
ON C.R.A.S.H. DAYS.

14:27.600 --> 14:30.403
SO, WHAT, YOU GOING
BACK TO DOING REAL
POLICE WORK NOW OR WHAT?

14:30.437 --> 14:32.940
I'M ROLLING WITH
GANG ENFORCEMENT DETAIL.

14:32.973 --> 14:34.541
HOP IN A CAR.
THERE YOU GO.

14:34.574 --> 14:36.676
MAKE THE ROUNDS.
Sal:
YOU SURE THAT'S A GOOD IDEA?

14:36.709 --> 14:38.411
HEY, I'LL SEE YOU
OUT THERE, SAM.

14:38.445 --> 14:40.413
HEY, SAL.
HEY, CHUCK.

14:40.447 --> 14:42.415
IT'S ONLY BEEN
SIX WEEKS.

14:42.449 --> 14:45.418
NOTHING WRONG WITH ROLLING SLOW
FOR A WHILE.

14:45.452 --> 14:48.421
THEY NEED TO SEE
THAT THEY DIDN'T WIN.

14:48.455 --> 14:51.291
AMEN.

14:51.324 --> 14:53.360
GONNA HAVE TO SHAVE THAT PEACH
FUZZ OFF YOUR FACE, THOUGH.

14:53.393 --> 14:55.162
NO WAY SERGEANT MILLER

14:55.195 --> 14:57.297
IS GONNA LET YOU OUT ON
THE STREETS LOOKING LIKE THAT,

14:57.330 --> 14:59.199
EVEN THOUGH YOU ARE
JUST A GUEST.

14:59.232 --> 15:01.168
HE'S OLD-SCHOOL.

15:01.201 --> 15:04.171
I LIKE IT, AND ANYBODY
THAT'S GOT A PROBLEM WITH IT,

15:04.204 --> 15:05.572
THEY KNOW WHERE TO FIND ME.

15:05.605 --> 15:07.274
SEE YOU LATER, SAL.

15:09.209 --> 15:11.678
HEY, SAMMY.

15:16.616 --> 15:19.352
[ DOOR OPENS ]

15:25.125 --> 15:27.394
DAMN!
LOOK AT THIS.

15:27.427 --> 15:29.196
[ LAUGHS ]
WHAT?

15:29.229 --> 15:32.399
CHECK YOU OUT, GIRL, WORKING
YOUR INNER NAOMI CAMPBELL.

15:32.432 --> 15:34.334
STOP.
[ LAUGHING ]

15:34.367 --> 15:38.071
AWW, IF YOU WEREN'T BLACK,
YOU'D BE BRIGHT RED.

15:38.105 --> 15:39.739
SHOULD HAVE WORN
MY GREEN BLOUSE.

15:39.772 --> 15:41.341
MM-HMM. YEAH.

15:41.374 --> 15:44.344
Woman: YOU GOT 30 MESSAGES,
ALL FROM MEDIA RELATIONS.

15:44.377 --> 15:45.645
FOR WHAT?

15:45.678 --> 15:47.480
INTERVIEW REQUESTS.

15:47.514 --> 15:50.283
THEY ALREADY HAD ME TALK
TO SCOTT GLOVER AT THE TIMES.

15:50.317 --> 15:53.520
E!, CNN, ESSENCE, EBONY,
THE NEW YORKER.

15:53.553 --> 15:56.489
JET WANTS TO FEATURE YOU
IN THIS WEEK'S BEST PHOTOS.

15:56.523 --> 15:58.491
WOW. JET?

15:58.525 --> 16:01.161
[ Laughing ]
MY GRANDMA'S GONNA FLIP.

16:01.194 --> 16:02.495
OH, GIRL, YOU GO.

16:02.529 --> 16:05.032
COME ON.
GIVE ME THAT NAOMI.

16:05.065 --> 16:06.266
OH, GOSH, STOP.

16:06.299 --> 16:08.268
I DON'T THINK
BILLY STEARN DID IT.

16:08.301 --> 16:09.569
OH, COME ON.

16:09.602 --> 16:11.638
THAT GUY COULD CHARM
THE PANTIES OFF A NUN.

16:11.671 --> 16:13.506
COME ON, LYDIA,
HE'S AN ACTOR.

16:13.540 --> 16:16.576
THAT'S WHY HE WAS MAKING
ALL THAT EYE CONTACT WITH YOU.

16:16.609 --> 16:18.378
YEAH, BUT HIS GIRLS
WERE THERE,

16:18.411 --> 16:20.247
AND SHE WAS COKED UP
ALL THE TIME.

16:20.280 --> 16:22.282
WHEN WE GOT THERE, THEY ASKED
FOR DADDY, NOT MOMMY.

16:22.315 --> 16:23.583
THAT'S MOTIVE.

16:23.616 --> 16:25.552
THAT'S WHY HE KILLED HER --
FOR THEM.

16:25.585 --> 16:27.520
I DON'T CARE
HOW MAD HE WAS AT HER.

16:27.554 --> 16:29.522
I DON'T SEE HIM
CUTTING OFF HER HEAD

16:29.556 --> 16:32.192
AND GOING ALL "KUNG FU PANDA"
ON THE BODYGUARD.

16:32.225 --> 16:33.693
CAN YOU IMAGINE
THE SCREAMS

16:33.726 --> 16:36.129
WITH HIS GIRLS RIGHT THERE
IN THE HOUSE?

16:36.163 --> 16:38.465
[ SIGHS ] I DON'T HAVE TO
IMAGINE IT, LYDIA.

16:38.498 --> 16:39.799
WE SAW WHAT HE DID.

16:39.832 --> 16:41.534
STILL DOESN'T MATCH UP.

16:41.568 --> 16:43.536
HEY, GORGEOUS.

16:43.570 --> 16:45.305
JUST QUOTING
THE BLOGGERS.

16:45.338 --> 16:47.307
THIS IS NINA BROWN,
BETHANY'S DIVORCE ATTORNEY.

16:47.340 --> 16:50.143
HELLO.
SHE HAS SOMETHING
SHE WANTS YOU TO HEAR.

16:50.177 --> 16:51.711
IS THERE A PRIVATE PLACE
WE CAN TALK?

16:51.744 --> 16:53.813
IT'S SECURE HERE.

16:53.846 --> 16:56.483
BOTH PARTIES HAD AGREED
TO A $25 MILLION SETTLEMENT.

16:56.516 --> 16:58.418
BILLY WOULD GET CASH
FROM BETHANY.

16:58.451 --> 17:00.287
BETHANY WAS GONNA GET
FULL CUSTODY.

17:00.320 --> 17:02.355
WITH HER GONE,
HE GETS IT ALL.

17:02.389 --> 17:03.590
THE GIRLS?

17:03.623 --> 17:06.559
AND HER ENTIRE
$300 MILLION FORTUNE --

17:06.593 --> 17:09.096
HER ESTATE, THE ROYALTIES
FROM HER RECORDS,

17:09.129 --> 17:11.364
CLOTHING, DOLLS,
PERFUME LINE, EVERYTHING.

17:11.398 --> 17:13.500
I CAN'T STAND THE BASTARD.

17:13.533 --> 17:16.503
I HOPE HE FRIES LIKE AN EGG
AT SAN QUENTIN.

17:16.536 --> 17:18.171
Billy: BITCH, PICK UP
THE GODDAMN PHONE!

17:18.205 --> 17:20.107
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU CAN'T SPEAK

17:20.140 --> 17:21.774
'CAUSE YOU GOT THAT LIMEY'S
DICK IN YOUR MOUTH!

17:21.808 --> 17:26.113
I SEE YOU RIGHT THROUGH
THE WINDOW.

17:26.146 --> 17:27.714
OUR KIDS ARE UPSTAIRS ASLEEP,
BITCH.

17:27.747 --> 17:29.449
DON'T YOU HAVE ANY DECENCY?

17:29.482 --> 17:31.584
I'LL GUT YOU
LIKE A GODDAMN FISH,

17:31.618 --> 17:33.120
YOU TROUT-MOUTHED BITCH!

17:42.862 --> 17:45.398
HE'S NOT SLEEPING.
HE MAY NOT BE GUILTY.

17:45.432 --> 17:49.402
OH, THAT'S A HOMICIDAL
OLD WIVES' TALE.

17:49.436 --> 17:51.371
Russell:
HEY, SUPERSTAR.

17:51.404 --> 17:52.705
Lydia: STOP.

17:52.739 --> 17:54.274
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:54.307 --> 17:55.542
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

17:55.575 --> 17:57.444
JUST WANTED TO SEE
THE BASTARD,

17:57.477 --> 17:59.546
JUST LOOK AT HIM
FOR A MINUTE.

18:02.182 --> 18:04.784
DETECTIVE OCHOA,
DO WE HAVE A PROBLEM?

18:04.817 --> 18:07.120
YEAH. I DON'T LIKE YOU
VERY MUCH.

18:07.154 --> 18:09.422
ANY PARTICULAR REASON?

18:09.456 --> 18:11.424
NO, NOT REALLY.

18:11.458 --> 18:13.460
NO?
MM.

18:13.493 --> 18:15.528
OH, COME ON!

18:15.562 --> 18:18.265
WE KNOW HE'S GUILTY.
WE JUST DON'T HAVE ENOUGH?

18:18.298 --> 18:20.300
I GUESS HE JUST WALKS.

18:20.333 --> 18:21.601
HE [BLEEP]
CHOPPED HER HEAD OFF!

18:21.634 --> 18:22.802
HE'S GONNA SLEEP
IN HIS OWN BED?!

18:22.835 --> 18:24.337
RUSS...

18:24.371 --> 18:26.206
NO! HE'S GONNA BE PLAYING
"CALL OF DUTY"

18:26.239 --> 18:28.275
AND GETTING A [BLEEP] HANDJOB
LESS THAN 18 HOURS

18:28.308 --> 18:29.876
AFTER HE SLAUGHTERED
HIS KIDS' MOTHER.

18:29.909 --> 18:31.711
[BLEEP] THIS.

18:31.744 --> 18:33.446
WHAT'S WRONG WITH HIM?

18:33.480 --> 18:35.582
HE'S ACTING LIKE
IT'S HIS CASE.

18:35.615 --> 18:38.351
HE JUST GETS WRAPPED UP
INTO THE VICTIMS,

18:38.385 --> 18:40.420
ESPECIALLY
WHEN THEY'RE WOMEN.

18:40.453 --> 18:43.356
HEY, YOU SURE YOU TWO
NEVER, UM...

18:43.390 --> 18:44.624
YEAH. NO.

18:44.657 --> 18:46.259
I-I'M SURE WE NEVER.

18:53.600 --> 18:57.437
SERGEANT BROWN TELLS ME
YOU USED TO WORK IN C.R.A.S.H.

18:57.470 --> 18:59.372
WOW.

18:59.406 --> 19:02.642
HE STILL TELLS WAR STORIES
ABOUT YOU IN THE OLD DAYS.

19:05.745 --> 19:08.348
WHY YOU GOT US OVER
IN TRECE TERRITORY?

19:08.381 --> 19:09.616
USUALLY NOT OVER HERE.

19:09.649 --> 19:10.917
FOUR TREY IS MY HOOD.

19:10.950 --> 19:13.653
ME, PERSONALLY, I LIKE
WORKING THE LATIN GANGS.

19:13.686 --> 19:14.887
THEY'RE ALL BUSINESS.

19:14.921 --> 19:16.923
THEY RESPECT THE BADGE
A LITTLE.

19:16.956 --> 19:20.393
IT'S ALWAYS WORSE WITH THE
BROTHERS WHEN YOU'RE A BROTHER.

19:20.427 --> 19:21.761
NO OFFENSE.

19:21.794 --> 19:25.465
ALWAYS TALKING CRAP
WHEN YOU JAM THEM UP.

19:25.498 --> 19:27.500
"SELL OUT"...

19:27.534 --> 19:29.602
"UNCLE TOM"...

19:29.636 --> 19:31.504
"OREO."

19:31.538 --> 19:34.607
THE OLDER ONES ALWAYS GOT
A NICKNAME FOR YOU.

19:34.641 --> 19:38.345
THEY USED TO CALL YOU PACMAN,
RIGHT?

19:38.378 --> 19:41.381
I SEE THAT.

19:41.414 --> 19:43.750
GOT THAT SEAN PENN,

19:43.783 --> 19:46.619
"CRAZY WHITE BOY" THING
GOING FOR YOU.

19:46.653 --> 19:48.888
YOU EVER SHUT UP?

19:48.921 --> 19:50.523
HELL NO.

19:50.557 --> 19:53.226
YOU KNOW HOW BORING
THIS JOB CAN BE?

19:53.260 --> 19:54.827
STOP.

19:54.861 --> 19:56.529
STOP!

19:58.531 --> 19:59.799
Damon: SAMMY!

19:59.832 --> 20:01.468
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

20:07.440 --> 20:10.510
DISPATCHER:
Any available units, please
respond to a report of a 211

20:10.543 --> 20:11.811
at 4301 Hoffman Place.

20:11.844 --> 20:13.246
Any available units.

20:13.280 --> 20:15.248
SECOND TIME
I HEARD THAT CALL.

20:15.282 --> 20:17.284
THIRD TIME.

20:17.317 --> 20:19.586
NO ONE'S
GONNA ANSWER IT.

20:19.619 --> 20:21.788
WE DON'T HAVE
THE MANPOWER.

20:21.821 --> 20:23.990
THOSE OF US
THAT AREN'T ON...

20:24.023 --> 20:27.827
MANDATORY DAYS OFF ARE CAUGHT UP
WITH THIS BULLSHIT.

20:29.862 --> 20:31.598
[ GRUNTING ]

20:36.836 --> 20:38.671
[ BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:38.705 --> 20:40.540
PUT YOUR HANDS
ON YOUR HEAD.

20:40.573 --> 20:41.741
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:41.774 --> 20:43.743
LOCK YOUR FINGERS
TOGETHER!

20:43.776 --> 20:45.812
LET ME SEE THEM.

20:45.845 --> 20:48.014
[ SIREN WAILS IN DISTANCE ]

20:48.047 --> 20:51.017
ALL RIGHT.

20:51.050 --> 20:54.020
OKAY, TURN AROUND SLOWLY.

20:54.053 --> 20:56.456
SLOWLY.

21:03.463 --> 21:04.964
WHAT'S YOUR STREET NAME?

21:04.997 --> 21:06.699
THEY CALL ME DOOBIE.

21:06.733 --> 21:09.469
YEAH?
WHERE YOU FROM, DOOBIE?

21:09.502 --> 21:11.738
I'M FROM MAIN STREET TRECE.

21:11.771 --> 21:14.741
YOU MESS WITH THE BEST,
AND YOU DIE LIKE THE REST.

21:14.774 --> 21:17.477
YOU WERE THERE
THAT NIGHT.
WHAT?

21:17.510 --> 21:19.045
YOU WERE [BLEEP] THERE
THAT [BLEEP] NIGHT!

21:19.078 --> 21:21.714
[BLEEP]
YOU SAY "WHAT" AGAIN!

21:21.748 --> 21:23.783
YOU KNOW THAT YOU CAN DROWN
IN AN INCH OF WATER?

21:23.816 --> 21:26.753
IF YOU'D HAVE STAYED IN SCHOOL,
YOU WOULD HAVE LEARNED THAT.

21:26.786 --> 21:28.054
[BLEEP]

21:28.087 --> 21:29.922
[ GRUNTING ]

21:29.956 --> 21:31.491
WERE YOU THERE
THAT NIGHT?!
WHERE?!

21:35.928 --> 21:37.930
[ GASPING ]
WERE YOU THERE?!

21:37.964 --> 21:40.600
YEAH! YEAH!

21:40.633 --> 21:41.868
[ GASPING ]

21:41.901 --> 21:44.003
LOOK AT ME.

21:44.036 --> 21:46.773
OPEN YOUR EYES
AND LOOK IN MY EYES.

21:46.806 --> 21:49.409
YOU THINK BY KILLING MY PARTNER,
YOU CAN RUN ME OFF?

21:49.442 --> 21:51.411
WHEN YOU WAKE UP,
YOU'RE GONNA SEE ME.

21:51.444 --> 21:53.513
WHEN YOU GO TO SLEEP,
YOU'RE GONNA SEE ME.

21:53.546 --> 21:55.682
I'M YOUR WORST [BLEEP]
NIGHTMARE.

21:55.715 --> 21:57.650
YOU TELL ALL OF THE REST
I'M BACK!

21:57.684 --> 21:59.786
SAMMY BRYANT IS BACK!
YOU HEAR ME?!

21:59.819 --> 22:02.355
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

22:02.389 --> 22:05.091
I'M BACK [BLEEP]

22:05.124 --> 22:06.793
Damon: BRYANT!

22:06.826 --> 22:10.430
[ PANTING ]

22:10.463 --> 22:14.367
TRYING TO GET US
GREENLIT?

22:14.401 --> 22:15.835
HERE YOU ARE.

22:15.868 --> 22:17.637
OH, WE DIDN'T
ORDER THESE.

22:17.670 --> 22:20.507
OH, THEY'RE ACTUALLY
FROM THE GENTLEMAN AT TABLE 7.

22:20.540 --> 22:22.775
HE, UH --
HE SAID HE SAW YOU IN THE PAPER.

22:22.809 --> 22:24.811
AND THERE'S A NOTE, TOO.

22:27.680 --> 22:28.815
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:33.420 --> 22:35.788
[ SIGHS ]
OH, COME ON.

22:35.822 --> 22:37.457
YOU'RE IN THE SPOTLIGHT.
ENJOY IT.

22:37.490 --> 22:38.791
ENJOY WHAT?

22:38.825 --> 22:40.660
ONE MORE BRIEFING,
AND R.H.D. TAKES IT.

22:40.693 --> 22:42.128
WHAT DOES THAT
HAVE TO DO

22:42.161 --> 22:44.831
WITH THAT FINE MAN OVER THERE
STARING AT YOU?

22:44.864 --> 22:47.934
YOU BETTER JUMP ON THAT SHIP
BEFORE IT SAILS, GIRL.

22:47.967 --> 22:49.569
OH, LET IT SAIL.

22:49.602 --> 22:50.937
COME ON, LYD.

22:50.970 --> 22:53.940
ALL THIS LOVE STUFF
IS GETTING ON MY NERVES.

22:53.973 --> 22:55.942
ALL RIGHT, SO,
WHY DON'T YOU DATE A COP?

22:55.975 --> 22:59.679
I DON'T WANT TO
TALK SHOP IN BED EVERY NIGHT

22:59.712 --> 23:01.548
BEFORE GOING TO SLEEP.

23:01.581 --> 23:03.850
GIRL, WHEN I'M WITH MY MAN,
WE DON'T DO MUCH TALKING.

23:03.883 --> 23:05.685
HIS MOUTH'S TOO BUSY.

23:05.718 --> 23:07.954
OOH! NASTY.

23:07.987 --> 23:09.556
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

23:09.589 --> 23:11.424
Man: ...THROUGH
THE EXEMPLARY REPORTING

23:11.458 --> 23:12.892
OF OUR EMMY-WINNING I-Team

23:12.925 --> 23:15.562
THAT WE ARE ABLE TO BRING YOU
EXCLUSIVE IMAGES

23:15.595 --> 23:17.597
YOU WON'T SEE
ANYWHERE ELSE...
WHAT IS IT?

23:17.630 --> 23:19.699
...PHOTOS FROM THE
BETHANY SANDERS MURDER SCENE.

23:19.732 --> 23:21.434
POLICE SOURCES SUSPECT
THAT BILLY STEARN,

23:21.468 --> 23:22.969
WHO RECEIVED SWORD TRAINING

23:23.002 --> 23:25.838
WHILE PREPARING FOR HIS
"SHOGUN ASSASSIN" REBOOT,

23:25.872 --> 23:29.442
HAD THE TRAINING AND THE MOTIVE
TO INFLICT SUCH DAMAGE

23:29.476 --> 23:31.444
ON THE SINGER AND HER LOVER.

23:31.478 --> 23:33.846
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?
Woman:
A LATE-BREAKING EXCLUSIVE --

23:33.880 --> 23:36.015
A VOICEMAIL LEFT BY
BILLY STEARN TO
BETHANY SANDERS,

23:36.048 --> 23:38.651
ANGRY ABOUT AN ALLEGED
SEXUAL ENCOUNTER

23:38.685 --> 23:40.787
WITH HER BODYGUARD,
CHARLES UPSON.

23:40.820 --> 23:42.855
[ CELLPHONES RINGING ]
HERE'S A PIECE OF IT,

23:42.889 --> 23:46.125
BUT BE WARNED --
IT'S GRAPHIC.
WOW.

23:46.158 --> 23:48.895
Billy: Bitch, pick up
the [bleep] phone!
HERE WE GO.

23:48.928 --> 23:50.530
[ VEHICLE DEPARTING ]

23:50.563 --> 23:53.600
I'M TELLING YOU,
YOU SHOULD SIT DOWN.

23:53.633 --> 23:57.203
JOB CALLED FOR A CHAIR,
THEY'D HAVE GAVE ME ONE.

23:57.236 --> 23:59.071
IT'S PART OF THE JOB --

23:59.105 --> 24:01.073
YOU STAND
WHERE THEY TELL YOU...

24:01.107 --> 24:02.509
[ SIGHS ]

24:02.542 --> 24:05.044
...FOR HOWEVER LONG
THEY TELL YOU.

24:05.077 --> 24:07.880
[ SIGHS ]

24:07.914 --> 24:10.016
SHOULD HAVE STAYED HOME
IF YOU'RE GONNA

24:10.049 --> 24:12.619
PLAY ON THAT THING ALL DAY
LIKE A TEENAGE GIRL.

24:12.652 --> 24:14.053
DID YOU HEAR THIS?

24:14.086 --> 24:16.155
OLIVIA JUST TEXTED IT
TO ME.

24:16.188 --> 24:19.025
BILLY: I'll gut you
like a goddamn fish,
you trout-mouthed bitch!

24:19.058 --> 24:21.160
AND NOW IT'S A RINGTONE.

24:21.193 --> 24:24.964
* I'll gut-gut-gut-
gut-gut-gut-gut you *

24:24.997 --> 24:26.766
* Like a goddamn
fish, fish, fish *

24:26.799 --> 24:28.167
* Trout-mouth bitch -- *
SHUT IT OFF.

24:28.200 --> 24:30.036
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

24:30.069 --> 24:34.173
YOU KNOW HOW MANY DOMESTICS
I'VE SEEN TURN INTO MURDERS?

24:34.206 --> 24:36.543
PEOPLE DON'T LIKE IT,
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:36.576 --> 24:37.844
PEOPLE FIGHT.

24:37.877 --> 24:39.546
THEY GET DRUNK,
THEY SAY NASTY THINGS,

24:39.579 --> 24:42.181
AND, YEAH,
THEY HIT EACH OTHER.

24:42.214 --> 24:43.850
YOU GET ONE [BLEEP] UP.

24:43.883 --> 24:46.919
THEY SHOULD HAVE
HAULED HIS ASS AWAY

24:46.953 --> 24:48.688
AFTER THE SECOND CALL-OUT.

24:48.721 --> 24:51.558
STRAIGHT TO JAIL,
JUST LIKE A D.U.I.

24:51.591 --> 24:54.193
[ TIRES SCREECHING,
METAL CRUNCHES ]

24:54.226 --> 24:56.228
JESUS.

24:56.262 --> 24:58.264
[ CAR DOOR BEEPING ]

25:00.733 --> 25:02.935
I STOPPED
10 FEET AHEAD OF YOU.

25:02.969 --> 25:04.937
IF YOU WEREN'T SO BUSY
LOOKING AT CARS

25:04.971 --> 25:06.573
AND PLAYING
WITH YOUR WALKMAN --

25:06.606 --> 25:08.074
I WAS FINE, OKAY?

25:08.107 --> 25:11.277
I HAVE MY BUDS IN BECAUSE
THAT'S HOW MY PHONE WORKS.

25:11.310 --> 25:12.979
GIVE IT UP.

25:16.182 --> 25:18.818
* I'll gut-gut-gut-
gut-gut-gut-gut you *

25:18.851 --> 25:21.120
* Like a goddamn
fish, fish, fish *

25:21.153 --> 25:23.956
* Trout-mouth
bitch, bitch, bitch! *
THAT'S JUST GREAT.

25:23.990 --> 25:26.826
WE'RE SITTING HERE
WITH OUR THUMBS UP OUR ASSES,

25:26.859 --> 25:29.562
AND BILLY STEARN
ALMOST KILLED TWO MORE PEOPLE.

25:29.596 --> 25:33.099
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

25:33.132 --> 25:34.701
THANK YOU.

25:34.734 --> 25:37.837
BE RIGHT BACK.

25:37.870 --> 25:39.906
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO FILL OUT
SOME PAPERWORK.

25:39.939 --> 25:41.908
[ HORN HONKS ]

25:41.941 --> 25:45.011
HELLO.

25:45.044 --> 25:46.913
TH-THIS IS --
THIS IS SAMMY BRYANT.

25:46.946 --> 25:49.215
YEAH. NO, YEAH, GO AHEAD.
I'M LISTENING.

25:52.819 --> 25:54.553
YOU'RE SURE?

25:57.624 --> 25:59.025
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

26:19.779 --> 26:22.682
LAB JUST CALLED.

26:22.715 --> 26:24.917
I'M GONNA BE A FATHER.

26:24.951 --> 26:28.354
YEAH?
I'M THE DAD.

26:35.327 --> 26:38.297
I'M THE DAD.
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:38.330 --> 26:40.132
[ HORN HONKING ]

26:44.236 --> 26:46.806
DETECTIVE ADAMS,
DETECTIVE OCHOA,

26:46.839 --> 26:49.075
MAY I SEE YOUR PHONES,
PLEASE?

26:49.108 --> 26:50.777
EXCUSE ME?

26:50.810 --> 26:52.679
DETECTIVES, YOUR PHONES.

26:54.947 --> 26:58.050
COMPUTER DIVISION SAYS THAT
THE PHOTOS THAT TMZ HAS

26:58.084 --> 27:00.186
DIDN'T COME FROM S.I.D.

27:00.219 --> 27:03.055
AND BECAUSE OF THEIR
HIGHER DIGITAL RESOLUTION,

27:03.089 --> 27:05.825
THEY'RE MORE CONSISTENT
WITH A SMARTPHONE.

27:05.858 --> 27:09.061
AND WE CHECKED WITH
EVERY PATROL OFFICER
AT THE SCENE THAT DAY,

27:09.095 --> 27:11.130
AS WELL AS
DETECTIVE WILSON'S PHONE.

27:11.163 --> 27:13.399
SO...

27:13.432 --> 27:15.668
DID EITHER OF YOU TAKE PICTURES
OF THE CRIME SCENE

27:15.702 --> 27:17.336
WITH YOUR OWN PHONE?

27:17.369 --> 27:18.838
ARE YOU TRYING TO SAY
WE LEAKED THIS?
LYDIA, CALM DOWN.

27:18.871 --> 27:21.007
HOW THE HELL
CAN I CALM DOWN?

27:21.040 --> 27:24.711
[ SIGHS ]

27:29.916 --> 27:33.285
LYDIA, DID YOU TAKE PICTURES
OF THE SANDERS CRIME SCENE

27:33.319 --> 27:34.887
WITH YOUR CELLPHONE?

27:37.156 --> 27:38.691
YES.

27:38.725 --> 27:40.693
[ SIGHS ]

27:40.727 --> 27:42.028
YOUR PHONE.

27:44.163 --> 27:48.167
I'M NOT GONNA ASK AGAIN.

27:48.200 --> 27:50.703
I UPLOADED THEM
TO MY COMPUTER

27:50.737 --> 27:52.271
LIKE I'VE DONE
HUNDREDS OF TIMES,

27:52.304 --> 27:54.741
BUT I DIDN'T GIVE THEM
OR ANYTHING TO THE PRESS.

27:54.774 --> 27:56.242
YOU'RE OFF THE CASE.

27:56.275 --> 27:58.845
IF R.H.D.
NEEDS ANYTHING ELSE,

27:58.878 --> 28:01.113
I WANT YOU TO CONTACT
DETECTIVE OCHOA.

28:01.147 --> 28:03.015
AM I SUSPENDED?
NO.

28:03.049 --> 28:05.151
I.E.D.'s GONNA CONDUCT
ITS OWN INVESTIGATION.

28:05.184 --> 28:07.686
I SUGGEST YOU CONTACT
A UNION REP.

28:09.288 --> 28:10.857
SHOULD I GO HOME?

28:10.890 --> 28:12.391
CATCH UP ON SOME
ADMINISTRATIVE PAPERWORK

28:12.424 --> 28:15.027
ON OPEN CASE FILES
AT YOUR DESK.

28:23.335 --> 28:24.904
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

28:31.343 --> 28:32.779
OH.

28:32.812 --> 28:34.013
MAY I HELP YOU?

28:37.283 --> 28:40.853
MOVE THE [BLEEP] BARRICADE!
THIS IS MY HOUSE!

28:40.887 --> 28:42.188
YEAH, ALL RIGHT.
GO AHEAD.

28:42.221 --> 28:44.090
HE'S GOOD.

28:49.829 --> 28:51.197
YOU HEAR THAT?

28:51.230 --> 28:53.065
IT'S BILLY STEARN.

28:53.099 --> 28:55.134
SO, HE'S OUT ON BAIL.

28:55.167 --> 28:56.468
I GUESS SO.

28:56.502 --> 28:58.805
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]
UH-OH.

28:58.838 --> 29:00.206
[BLEEP] THIS SHIT.

29:00.239 --> 29:03.075
DISPATCHER:
Any available unit to handle.

29:03.109 --> 29:07.146
P.R. reports unusual odor coming
from 6901 Lennox Street.

29:07.179 --> 29:08.981
BUY IT.

29:09.015 --> 29:11.818
IT'S PROBABLY
JUST A D.B. CALL.
I DON'T CARE.

29:11.851 --> 29:13.820
PROBABLY A HUNDRED 911 CALLS
GOT IGNORED TODAY

29:13.853 --> 29:15.487
BECAUSE OF THIS POP SINGER
GETTING MURDERED

29:15.521 --> 29:17.256
BY HER DRUG-ADDICTED
EX-HUSBAND,

29:17.289 --> 29:18.991
AND THIS PIECE OF SHIT --
HE'S NOT GONNA EVEN SPEND

29:19.025 --> 29:20.893
ONE NIGHT IN JAIL
FOR WHAT HE DID.

29:20.927 --> 29:23.362
AND THE WATCH COMMANDER?
WHAT'S HE GONNA DO,
ARREST ME?

29:23.395 --> 29:25.264
YOU DRIVE.

29:26.999 --> 29:28.500
A43,
SHOW US HANDLING.

29:28.534 --> 29:31.070
[ SHOUTING CONTINUES ]

29:36.075 --> 29:38.811
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

30:02.034 --> 30:04.336
THESE ARE MY BABIES --

30:04.370 --> 30:07.206
CARTER AND KEEGAN.

30:17.383 --> 30:20.019
I FOLLOW
THE PATROLMAN'S CREED --

30:20.052 --> 30:23.289
MAKE IT HOME ALIVE,
WHATEVER IT TAKES,

30:23.322 --> 30:27.293
TO THE WIFE,
YOUR GIRLFRIEND...

30:27.326 --> 30:30.096
OR, IN SOME CASES, BOTH.

30:30.129 --> 30:32.899
YOU SAYING
I GOT MY PARTNER KILLED?

30:32.932 --> 30:34.200
NO.

30:34.233 --> 30:36.936
BUT YOU'RE OUT HERE
PLAYING DENZEL,

30:36.969 --> 30:38.170
DUNKING BABY GANGSTERS?

30:38.204 --> 30:40.172
YOU SAYING
I GOT MY PARTNER KILLED?

30:40.206 --> 30:41.908
THERE ARE RULES
TO THIS SHIT.

30:41.941 --> 30:44.310
WE BOTH KNOW THAT.

30:44.343 --> 30:48.480
THEY KILL A COP,
WE KILL THEM.

30:48.514 --> 30:51.583
AND IT GOES
BACK AND FORTH...

30:51.617 --> 30:53.352
AND IT WON'T STOP.

30:56.956 --> 30:59.926
I DON'T WANT MY BABIES
WEARING BLACK SUITS,

30:59.959 --> 31:02.094
HOLDING A FLAG
AT MY FUNERAL.

31:02.128 --> 31:05.264
LET'S GO.

31:05.297 --> 31:07.934
COME ON.
I'M DRIVING.

31:07.967 --> 31:11.137
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

31:16.375 --> 31:17.944
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

31:17.977 --> 31:20.046
[ DOGS BARKING ]

31:25.117 --> 31:27.286
YOU WANT SOME?
[ SNIFFS ]

31:33.659 --> 31:36.028
POLICE!

31:41.400 --> 31:44.636
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

31:44.670 --> 31:47.539
[ INDISTINCT TALKING
ON TELEVISION ]

31:51.543 --> 31:53.645
HELLO.

31:53.679 --> 31:56.983
IT NEVER FELT LIKE HOME.
POLICE.

31:57.016 --> 32:00.119
I MEAN, PAT WAS COOL,
BUT HE WAS ALWAYS WORKING.

32:00.152 --> 32:03.722
HALF THE TIME, MOM WAS
ZONKED OUT ON SLEEPING PILLS.

32:03.755 --> 32:05.457
THAT NAME -- KOEHLER...

32:05.491 --> 32:06.658
HELLO.

32:06.692 --> 32:08.327
...MEANT SOMETHING TO ME.

32:08.360 --> 32:11.263
IT WAS MY ONLY CONNECTION
TO MY DAD.

32:11.297 --> 32:14.233
MY MOM DID EVERYTHING SHE COULD
TO TAKE THAT AWAY FROM ME.

32:17.103 --> 32:19.405
I WANTED TO LOVE HER,
BUT SHE WAS COLD.

32:19.438 --> 32:22.141
SHE LOVED HER THINGS
MORE THAN SHE LOVED ME.

32:22.174 --> 32:25.211
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHERE
MY ACTING CAREER GOT STARTED?

32:25.244 --> 32:29.548
IT WAS FROM MAKING MYSELF SMILE
WHEN SHE KISSED ME GOOD NIGHT.

32:29.581 --> 32:35.621
Man:
STEARN'S CAREER DID START SOON
AFTER THAT BEFORE HE WAS 11.

32:35.654 --> 32:38.190
[ SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

32:42.594 --> 32:45.164
HEY.

32:45.197 --> 32:47.066
HEY.

32:47.099 --> 32:49.301
YOU OKAY?

32:49.335 --> 32:51.437
ALL RIGHT?

32:51.470 --> 32:55.107
GIVE ME YOUR HAND.

32:55.141 --> 32:57.376
CAN YOU GET UP?

32:57.409 --> 32:59.478
OKAY?
STAND UP FOR ME.

32:59.511 --> 33:01.713
STAND UP FOR ME.

33:01.747 --> 33:05.184
OKAY. ALL RIGHT.
OKAY.

33:05.217 --> 33:08.520
OKAY.

33:08.554 --> 33:10.256
OKAY.

33:10.289 --> 33:14.260
THIS WHERE IT HAPPEN?

33:14.293 --> 33:18.197
WE WERE DRIVING HOME.

33:18.230 --> 33:20.266
SOMEBODY THREW A BOTTLE.
IT WASN'T A BIG DEAL.

33:20.299 --> 33:21.467
YOU KNOW, HE COULD HAVE
LET IT GO,

33:21.500 --> 33:24.203
BUT NATE WASN'T LIKE THAT.

33:24.236 --> 33:26.772
I HAD A DIFFERENT ATTITUDE
ABOUT GANGS

33:26.805 --> 33:28.774
BEFORE I MET NATE --

33:28.807 --> 33:30.609
NIGHT STICKS, KIWI SHAMPOO.

33:30.642 --> 33:32.344
BUT NATE...

33:32.378 --> 33:34.246
HE GREW UP HERE.

33:34.280 --> 33:37.683
WHERE I SAW ASSHOLES,
HE SAW KIDS.

33:37.716 --> 33:40.486
BUT, UM...

33:40.519 --> 33:42.154
YOU KNOW,
HE -- HE TALKED TO PEOPLE.

33:42.188 --> 33:43.489
HE TAUGHT ME
THAT IF YOU...

33:43.522 --> 33:46.092
IF YOU TREAT THEM
WITH RESPECT

33:46.125 --> 33:48.760
THAT TH-TH-THEY'LL TALK TO YOU
WHEN YOU NEED THEM MOST.

33:48.794 --> 33:50.362
[ DOG BARKING ]

33:50.396 --> 33:52.331
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

33:55.334 --> 33:57.669
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

33:57.703 --> 33:59.805
IT WAS JUST A BOTTLE,
YOU KNOW?

33:59.838 --> 34:01.407
I COULD HAVE LET IT GO.

34:01.440 --> 34:03.242
COULD HAVE LET IT GO.

34:03.275 --> 34:05.544
THEY CAME FROM EVERYWHERE.
THERE WAS --

34:05.577 --> 34:09.315
[ Voice breaking ]
ONE OF THEM HAD A...PIPE.

34:09.348 --> 34:11.250
HIT HIM HERE.

34:11.283 --> 34:13.452
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

34:13.485 --> 34:16.588
I HAD FIVE GUYS ON ME,
KICKING.

34:18.290 --> 34:20.559
I WANTED TO GET TO HIM,
I TRIED TO GET TO HIM,

34:20.592 --> 34:22.528
BUT I COULDN'T GET
TO HIM. I --

34:22.561 --> 34:24.396
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

34:24.430 --> 34:26.298
I SAW ONE OF THEM
REACH FOR THE GUN,

34:26.332 --> 34:27.399
AND THAT'S WHERE I FIRED.

34:27.433 --> 34:28.700
Damon: GEORGE 33.

34:28.734 --> 34:31.870
SHOW US CODE 6
AT WITMER AND LYNWOOD.

34:31.903 --> 34:34.140
REQUESTING BACKUP.

34:34.173 --> 34:36.208
HE TREATED THESE ASSHOLES
LIKE PEOPLE.

34:36.242 --> 34:37.409
THEY KILLED HIM FOR IT.

34:37.443 --> 34:38.744
IT WAS A RIGHTEOUS SHOOT.

34:38.777 --> 34:41.280
HELL, YOU COULD HAVE
KILLED SIX OF THEM,

34:41.313 --> 34:43.482
AND IT STILL WOULD HAVE
BEEN RIGHTEOUS.

34:43.515 --> 34:46.818
THEY'LL PROBABLY GIVE YOU
THE MEDAL OF VALOR.

34:46.852 --> 34:49.688
I DON'T WANT
A [BLEEP] MEDAL.

34:49.721 --> 34:52.291
THAT'S HIM!

34:52.324 --> 34:54.626
[ SIREN WAILS IN DISTANCE ]

35:02.201 --> 35:03.702
YOU KNOW
WHERE YOU'RE AT?

35:03.735 --> 35:04.903
YEAH.

35:04.936 --> 35:06.438
DO YOU?

35:06.472 --> 35:08.607
YOU GOT ABOUT 30 SECONDS
TO GET IN YOUR CAR.

35:08.640 --> 35:10.209
YOU KILLED MY PARTNER.

35:10.242 --> 35:13.712
OR LET SOMEONE
FROM THE TRECE DO IT.

35:13.745 --> 35:17.516
I'M COMING
FOR EVERYTHING YOU GOT.

35:17.549 --> 35:19.651
I AIN'T GOING ANYWHERE.

35:19.685 --> 35:22.321
YOU HEAR ME?
I AIN'T GOING ANYWHERE.

35:22.354 --> 35:23.655
SAMMY, SAMMY.
NOWHERE.

35:23.689 --> 35:25.624
I'M GONNA BE RIGHT HERE!
COME ON.

35:25.657 --> 35:27.726
I AIN'T GOING ANYWHERE.
YOU HEAR ME?

35:27.759 --> 35:29.728
Damon: Y'ALL GO ON BACK
TO YOUR HOMES.

35:29.761 --> 35:31.397
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE!

35:33.265 --> 35:35.634
NOT GOING ANYWHERE, MAN.

35:35.667 --> 35:38.204
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

35:45.977 --> 35:48.247
[ SIGHS ]

35:51.783 --> 35:54.486
THINK IT WAS JOSIE?

35:54.520 --> 35:56.822
NOT EVERYONE'S
OUT TO GET YOU, LYDIA.

35:56.855 --> 35:59.458
[ SIGHS ] R.H.D.?

35:59.491 --> 36:01.327
JUST GO HOME.

36:03.729 --> 36:05.597
16 YEARS.

36:05.631 --> 36:09.701
SOUTHEAST, NARCO, GANGS.

36:09.735 --> 36:13.339
I PROTECTED THAT LITTLE GIRL.
IT WASN'T EVEN MY CASE.

36:13.372 --> 36:15.707
THEY SHOT UP
MY MOM'S HOUSE.

36:15.741 --> 36:17.309
[ SIGHS ]

36:17.343 --> 36:21.480
AND NOW THEY WANT TO ACCUSE ME
OF BEING DISLOYAL?

36:21.513 --> 36:24.216
IT'S SMOKE. NO FIRE.

36:24.250 --> 36:25.584
THEY'RE GONNA RUN
YOUR FINANCIALS,

36:25.617 --> 36:26.885
THEY'RE GONNA SEARCH
YOUR COMPUTER,

36:26.918 --> 36:28.454
AND THEY'RE NOT GONNA FIND
ANYTHING

36:28.487 --> 36:31.223
'CAUSE YOU DIDN'T DO
ANYTHING.

36:31.257 --> 36:32.524
YOU'LL BE FINE.

36:35.761 --> 36:39.365
WHAT IF
I'M NOT A COP, RUSS?

36:39.398 --> 36:42.601
ALL I GOT IS THIS JOB.

36:42.634 --> 36:44.670
[ SIREN WAILS IN DISTANCE ]

36:44.703 --> 36:46.872
YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE.

36:46.905 --> 36:48.674
AND, YOU KNOW,

36:48.707 --> 36:51.610
AFTER YOU GET OVER THE FACT
THAT YOU CAN GET KILLED,

36:51.643 --> 36:55.947
THERE'S ONLY TWO THINGS
YOU WORRY ABOUT ON THIS JOB --

36:55.981 --> 36:58.517
YOU WORRY YOU'RE NOT GONNA
BE THERE FOR YOUR PARTNER

36:58.550 --> 36:59.951
IF SOMETHING HAPPENS
TO THEM...

37:01.787 --> 37:04.290
...AND IF THE DEPARTMENT
IS GONNA HANG YOU OUT TO DRY

37:04.323 --> 37:06.492
'CAUSE SOMETHING DOESN'T FALL
THE WAY THEY LIKE.

37:06.525 --> 37:07.959
[ SIGHS ]

37:07.993 --> 37:10.629
Russell: THAT'S NOT
GONNA HAPPEN. IT'S NOT.

37:10.662 --> 37:13.265
OKAY?

37:13.299 --> 37:16.802
THAT AIN'T GONNA HAPPEN.

37:20.306 --> 37:22.641
GO HOME.

37:22.674 --> 37:24.443
I'LL CALL YOU.

37:36.822 --> 37:38.990
[ SIGHS ]

37:39.024 --> 37:40.926
[ INDISTINCT TALKING
ON TELEVISION ]

37:40.959 --> 37:42.994
Man: IT WAS ON
THE "WILD BUNCH" REMAKE

37:43.028 --> 37:45.531
THAT BOTH SANDERS AND STEARN
WERE SMITTEN.

37:45.564 --> 37:47.533
THREE DAYS.

37:47.566 --> 37:49.835
EATING WHAT WAS LEFT
IN THE REFRIGERATOR.

37:49.868 --> 37:51.737
HEART ATTACK.
THE KID DIDN'T EVEN LEAVE.

37:51.770 --> 37:53.339
JUST STAYED THERE.

37:53.372 --> 37:55.607
WHERE'S HE GONNA GO?

37:55.641 --> 37:59.578
THE MOTHER'S HOOKED ON METH.
FATHER'S NOWHERE TO BE FOUND.

37:59.611 --> 38:01.547
YEAH.

38:01.580 --> 38:03.682
HE HAD THE TRAINING AND THE
MOTIVE TO INFLICT SUCH DAMAGE.

38:03.715 --> 38:05.484
TOO BAD KIDS
CAN'T PICK THEIR PARENTS.

38:05.517 --> 38:08.554
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

38:08.587 --> 38:10.456
WHY WEREN'T YOU GUYS
AT YOUR POST?

38:10.489 --> 38:11.990
[ SIGHS ]

38:12.023 --> 38:13.692
COOPER?

38:13.725 --> 38:15.827
STEARN EVENTUALLY
CLEANED UP HIS ACT...

38:15.861 --> 38:17.763
SARGE,
TH-THAT KID OUT THERE?

38:17.796 --> 38:19.965
..."GOOD GIRL GONE WILD" IMAGE
THAT SOLD MILLIONS OF ALBUMS...

38:19.998 --> 38:23.101
HE WAS WITH HIS DEAD
GRANDFATHER FOR THREE DAYS
EATING NOTHING BUT GARBAGE,

38:23.134 --> 38:25.371
ALL BECAUSE THE MAYOR CARES MORE
ABOUT CELEBRITIES

38:25.404 --> 38:26.638
THAN PEOPLE IN THIS TOWN.

38:26.672 --> 38:28.039
AND YOU WANT SOMEONE
TO GUARD A YARD,

38:28.073 --> 38:30.008
GET SOME EXPLORERS
WITH ORANGE TRAFFIC CONES,

38:30.041 --> 38:31.910
NOT REAL POLICE OFFICERS
WITH THINGS TO DO

38:31.943 --> 38:33.612
AND PEOPLE TO PROTECT.

38:33.645 --> 38:36.482
...MONITOR HER PROGRESS
24/7.

38:36.515 --> 38:38.650
GET BACK
TO BILLY STEARN'S HOUSE NOW.

38:38.684 --> 38:40.118
WHY?

38:40.151 --> 38:42.488
THEY JUST FOUND HIS BODY.

38:42.521 --> 38:44.055
WHAT HE DIDN'T COUNT ON

38:44.089 --> 38:47.426
WAS UPSON AND BETHANY
FALLING WILDLY IN LUST.

38:51.763 --> 38:53.765
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

39:15.687 --> 39:19.425
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

39:25.797 --> 39:28.099
Mariella:
COME ON, PETEY, TWO BITES.

39:28.133 --> 39:30.569
PLEASE?

39:30.602 --> 39:32.971
HE'S HERE!

39:35.941 --> 39:37.443
[ DOOR OPENS ]

39:37.476 --> 39:40.646
OHH!

39:40.679 --> 39:42.047
WHAT DO YOU GOT TO SAY?

39:42.080 --> 39:44.483
YOU'RE HOME.
YEAH?

39:46.618 --> 39:48.687
HEY.
HEY.

39:51.990 --> 39:53.925
HOW WAS IT?

39:53.959 --> 39:56.161
YOU GOT --
UH...

39:59.230 --> 40:04.202
UH, IT WAS OKAY.
IT WAS EMOTIONAL.

40:04.235 --> 40:06.872
YOU HUNGRY?

40:06.905 --> 40:08.474
OH, I'M STARVING.

40:08.507 --> 40:11.443
REALLY.
REAL HUNGRY.

40:11.477 --> 40:14.946
WELL, I WOULD HAVE
PACKED YOU LUNCH.

40:14.980 --> 40:16.948
[ SIGHS ]

40:16.982 --> 40:19.485
DO YOU WANT TACOS?

40:19.518 --> 40:20.786
MM...

40:25.123 --> 40:27.459
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING,
CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

40:27.493 --> 40:29.595
[ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

40:33.665 --> 40:36.468
SAVED A LOT OF MONEY
WITH THAT GUNSHOT.

40:36.502 --> 40:40.038
ROCKY BALBOA'S STILL GONNA
BE PISSED ABOUT HIS AZALEAS.

40:40.071 --> 40:41.740
THAT'S NOT OUR PROBLEM.

40:43.775 --> 40:46.111
THINK HE DID IT?

40:46.144 --> 40:47.913
SAID HE WAS INNOCENT
IN THE NOTE HE LEFT.

40:50.816 --> 40:54.152
I STILL THINK HE DID IT.

40:54.185 --> 40:55.887
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

40:55.921 --> 40:58.590
DISPATCHER: A43, see the woman,
unknown trouble.

40:58.624 --> 41:01.760
24356 Magnolia.

41:01.793 --> 41:04.129
LET'S GO DO
SOME REAL WORK.

41:04.162 --> 41:07.132
[ SIREN WAILS ]

41:07.165 --> 41:08.767
[ SIGHS ]

41:10.702 --> 41:13.204
WHAT'S EVEN MORE STUNNING
THAN STEARNS' SUICIDE

41:13.238 --> 41:16.642
IS THE FACT THAT HE MIGHT
BE INNOCENT AFTER ALL.

41:16.675 --> 41:19.645
HALF AN HOUR AGO,
POLICE ARRESTED THIS MAN,

41:19.678 --> 41:22.013
EX-MARINE SERGEANT
ROBERT MARION

41:22.047 --> 41:24.816
AT THE L.A.X. HERTZ RENT-A-CAR

41:24.850 --> 41:27.619
[ SIGHS ]
IN THE TRUNK OF HIS FORD FOCUS,
POLICE FOUND A SAMURAI SWORD,

41:27.653 --> 41:29.521
A PAIR OF BLOODY NIKES,

41:29.555 --> 41:33.291
AND A CAMERA WITH HUNDREDS
OF PHOTOS OF SANDERS AND UPSON

41:33.324 --> 41:33.391
TAKEN WITHOUT THEIR KNOWLEDGE.
